  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the granulated sugar, xanthous honey, vanilla extract, cinnamon, and salt.",
    "Add the eggs one at a time, whisking until smooth.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the heavy cream and cubed bread.",
    "Pour the cream-bread mixture into the sugar mixture and stir until combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Bake for 35-40 minutes or until the clafoutis is golden brown and set.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 10 minutes before serving."
